{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I just came back from a community"},{"time":2000,"text":"that holds the secret to human survival."},{"time":6000,"text":"It's a place where women run the show,"},{"time":9000,"text":"have sex to say hello,"},{"time":11000,"text":"and play rules the day --"},{"time":13000,"text":"where fun is serious business."},{"time":16000,"text":"And no, this isn't Burning Man"},{"time":18000,"text":"or San Francisco."},{"time":20000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":22000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, meet your cousins."},{"time":25000,"text":"This is the world of wild bonobos"},{"time":28000,"text":"in the jungles of Congo."},{"time":30000,"text":"Bonobos are, together with chimpanzees,"},{"time":33000,"text":"your living closest relative."},{"time":36000,"text":"That means we all share a common ancestor,"},{"time":39000,"text":"an evolutionary grandmother,"},{"time":41000,"text":"who lived around six million years ago."},{"time":45000,"text":"Now, chimpanzees are well-known"},{"time":47000,"text":"for their aggression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"But unfortunately,"},{"time":54000,"text":"we have made too much of an emphasis"},{"time":56000,"text":"of this aspect"},{"time":58000,"text":"in our narratives of human evolution."},{"time":61000,"text":"But bonobos show us"},{"time":63000,"text":"the other side of the coin."},{"time":65000,"text":"While chimpanzees"},{"time":67000,"text":"are dominated by big, scary guys,"},{"time":70000,"text":"bonobo society"},{"time":72000,"text":"is run by empowered females."},{"time":76000,"text":"These guys have really worked something out,"},{"time":79000,"text":"since this leads to a highly tolerant society"},{"time":82000,"text":"where fatal violence"},{"time":84000,"text":"has not been observed yet."},{"time":87000,"text":"But unfortunately,"},{"time":89000,"text":"bonobos are the least understood"},{"time":91000,"text":"of the great apes."},{"time":93000,"text":"They live in the depths of the Congolese jungle,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and it has been very difficult to study them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"The Congo is a paradox --"},{"time":102000,"text":"a land of extraordinary biodiversity and beauty,"},{"time":106000,"text":"but also the heart of darkness itself --"},{"time":109000,"text":"the scene of a violent conflict"},{"time":112000,"text":"that has raged for decades"},{"time":114000,"text":"and claimed nearly as many lives"},{"time":117000,"text":"as the First World War."},{"time":121000,"text":"Not surprisingly,"},{"time":123000,"text":"this destruction also endangers bonobo survival."},{"time":127000,"text":"Bushmeat trades and forest loss"},{"time":130000,"text":"means we couldn't fill a small stadium"},{"time":133000,"text":"with all the bonobos that are left in the world --"},{"time":135000,"text":"and we're not even sure of that to be honest."},{"time":139000,"text":"Yet, in this land of violence and chaos,"},{"time":143000,"text":"you can hear hidden laughter"},{"time":146000,"text":"swaying the trees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"Who are these cousins?"},{"time":151000,"text":"We know them as the \"make love, not war\" apes"},{"time":155000,"text":"since they have frequent, promiscuous"},{"time":157000,"text":"and bisexual sex"},{"time":159000,"text":"to manage conflict"},{"time":161000,"text":"and solve social issues."},{"time":163000,"text":"Now, I'm not saying this is the solution"},{"time":165000,"text":"to all of humanity's problems --"},{"time":169000,"text":"since there's more to bonobo life"},{"time":171000,"text":"than the Kama Sutra."},{"time":173000,"text":"Bonobos, like humans,"},{"time":175000,"text":"love to play throughout their entire lives."},{"time":177000,"text":"Play is not just child's games."},{"time":179000,"text":"For us and them,"},{"time":181000,"text":"play is foundational for bonding relationships"},{"time":184000,"text":"and fostering tolerance."},{"time":186000,"text":"It's where we learn to trust"},{"time":188000,"text":"and where we learn about the rules of the game."},{"time":191000,"text":"Play increases creativity"},{"time":193000,"text":"and resilience,"},{"time":196000,"text":"and it's all about the generation of diversity --"},{"time":199000,"text":"diversity of interactions,"},{"time":201000,"text":"diversity of behaviors,"},{"time":203000,"text":"diversity of connections."},{"time":206000,"text":"And when you watch bonobo play,"},{"time":208000,"text":"you're seeing the very evolutionary roots"},{"time":211000,"text":"of human laughter, dance"},{"time":213000,"text":"and ritual."},{"time":215000,"text":"Play is the glue"},{"time":217000,"text":"that binds us together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"Now, I don't know how you play,"},{"time":222000,"text":"but I want to show you a couple of unique clips"},{"time":224000,"text":"fresh from the wild."},{"time":226000,"text":"First, it's a ball game bonobo-style --"},{"time":229000,"text":"and I do not mean football."},{"time":232000,"text":"So here,"},{"time":234000,"text":"we have a young female and a male"},{"time":236000,"text":"engaged in a chase game."},{"time":239000,"text":"Have a look what she's doing."},{"time":241000,"text":"It might be the evolutionary origin of the phrase,"},{"time":243000,"text":"\"she's got him by the balls.\""},{"time":245000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":248000,"text":"Only I think that he's rather loving it here, right?"},{"time":252000,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":254000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":256000,"text":"So sex play is common"},{"time":258000,"text":"in both bonobos and humans."},{"time":260000,"text":"And this video is really interesting"},{"time":262000,"text":"because it shows --"},{"time":264000,"text":"this video's really interesting"},{"time":266000,"text":"because it shows the inventiveness"},{"time":268000,"text":"of bringing unusual elements into play --"},{"time":271000,"text":"such as testicles --"},{"time":274000,"text":"and also how play both requires trust"},{"time":277000,"text":"and fosters trust --"},{"time":280000,"text":"while at the same time being tremendous fun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"But play's a shapeshifter."},{"time":284000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":287000,"text":"Play's a shapeshifter,"},{"time":289000,"text":"and it can take many forms,"},{"time":291000,"text":"some of which are more quiet,"},{"time":293000,"text":"imaginative, curious --"},{"time":295000,"text":"maybe where wonder is discovered anew."},{"time":298000,"text":"And I want you to see,"},{"time":300000,"text":"this is Fuku, a young female,"},{"time":302000,"text":"and she is quietly playing with water."},{"time":304000,"text":"I think, like her,"},{"time":306000,"text":"we sometimes play alone,"},{"time":308000,"text":"and we explore the boundaries"},{"time":310000,"text":"of our inner and our outer worlds."},{"time":313000,"text":"And it's that playful curiosity"},{"time":315000,"text":"that drives us to explore, drives us to interact,"},{"time":319000,"text":"and then the unexpected connections we form"},{"time":322000,"text":"are the real hotbed for creativity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326000,"text":"So these are just small tasters"},{"time":329000,"text":"into the insights that bonobo give us"},{"time":331000,"text":"to our past and present."},{"time":334000,"text":"But they also hold a secret for our future,"},{"time":337000,"text":"a future where we need to adapt"},{"time":339000,"text":"to an increasingly challenging world"},{"time":342000,"text":"through greater creativity"},{"time":344000,"text":"and greater cooperation."},{"time":346000,"text":"The secret is that play is the key"},{"time":349000,"text":"to these capacities."},{"time":351000,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":353000,"text":"play is our adaptive wildcard."},{"time":355000,"text":"In order to adapt successfully"},{"time":357000,"text":"to a changing world,"},{"time":359000,"text":"we need to play."},{"time":363000,"text":"But will we make the most of our playfulness?"},{"time":366000,"text":"Play is not frivolous."},{"time":368000,"text":"Play's essential."},{"time":370000,"text":"For bonobos and humans alike,"},{"time":373000,"text":"life is not just red in tooth and claw."},{"time":376000,"text":"In times when it seems least appropriate to play,"},{"time":379000,"text":"it might be the times when it is most urgent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"And so, my fellow primates,"},{"time":386000,"text":"let us embrace this gift from evolution"},{"time":389000,"text":"and play together,"},{"time":391000,"text":"as we rediscover creativity,"},{"time":394000,"text":"fellowship and wonder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}